A '''ruling staff''' was a private accessory worn by a government leader primarily a [[Head of State/Legends|Head of State]]. Heirs of various [[King/Legends|Monarchies]] would receive their own ruling staffs as well in recognition of their future power.

[[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]], [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]], received her ruling staff on her [[Birthday/Legends|birthday]] from her father, [[Chief/Legends|Chief]] [[Chirpa/Legends|Chirpa]]. On that day Chirpa had chosen Kneesaa as the future Chief of their [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] tribe, and the staff symbolized this. Kneesaa´s staff was made from a branch of the rare [[Gemwood tree]].

Chief Chirpa used his ruling staff as a weapon, during the [[Battle of Bright Tree Village (Stranger War)|Battle of Bright Tree Village]].

